<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>PAYMU - Gaming Top-up Platform</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Montserrat:wght@700;800;900&display=swap');
        :root {
            --primary-color: #4F46E5; /* Indigo */
            --primary-hover: #4338CA;
            --secondary-color: #10B981; /* Emerald */
            --accent-color: #06B6D4; /* Cyan */
            --bg-color: #0F172A; /* Slate 900 */
            --card-bg: #1E293B; /* Slate 800 */
            --text-color: #F1F5F9; /* Slate 100 */
            --text-muted: #94A3B8; /* Slate 400 */
            --input-bg: #334155; /* Slate 700 */
            --success-color: #10B981; /* Emerald 500 */
            --error-color: #EF4444; /* Red 500 */
            --border-color: #475569; /* Slate 600 */
            --font-main: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            --font-display: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
        }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { 
            font-family: var(--font-main); 
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg-color) 0%, #131f38 100%);
            color: var(--text-color); 
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        header {
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .header-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 2em;
            font-weight: 900;
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        .logo i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .nav-links a {
            color: var(--text-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
        }
        .auth-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .btn {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer;
            border: none;
            font-family: var(--font-main);
        }
        .btn i {
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.3);
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(79, 70, 229, 0.4);
        }
        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            color: var(--text-color);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
        }
        .btn-outline:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .user-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 15px;
        }
        .user-balance {
            background-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            color: var(--success-color);
            padding: 8px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3);
        }
        .hero {
            padding: 80px 0 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 3em;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .hero-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }
        .hero-buttons .btn {
            padding: 14px 30px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        .games-section {
            padding: 40px 0 80px;
        }
        .section-title {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 2em;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
        }
        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -10px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--accent-color));
            border-radius: 3px;
        }
        .games-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(250px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .game-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--card-bg), #253654);
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            position: relative;
        }
        .game-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .game-image {
            width: 100%;
            height: 180px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .game-info {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .game-name {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .game-currency {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .game-card .btn {
            width: 100%;
        }
        .features-section {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background-color: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.5);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
        }
        .feature-card {
            background: linear-gradient(145deg, var(--card-bg), #253654);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .feature-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            border-color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .feature-icon {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            color: var(--accent-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .feature-title {
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 1.3em;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .feature-description {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        footer {
            padding: 40px 0;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
        }
        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .footer-links a {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: var(--accent-color);
        }
        .copyright {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9em;
        }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            .nav-links {
                margin: 15px 0;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2em;
            }
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1em;
            }
            .hero-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            .games-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            }
            .features-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .nav-links {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            .auth-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                width: 100%;
            }
            .user-info {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="header-content">
                <a href="/" class="logo"><i class="fas fa-bolt-lightning"></i> PAYMU</a>
                
                <nav class="nav-links">
                    <a href="/"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> Home</a>
                    <% if (user) { %>
                        <a href="/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-user"></i> Dashboard</a>
                        <a href="/transactions"><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Transaksi</a>
                    <% } %>
                    <a href="#games"><i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> Games</a>
                </nav>
                
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <div class="user-info">
                        <div class="user-balance">
                            <i class="fas fa-wallet"></i> Rp <%= user.balance.toLocaleString('id-ID') %>
                        </div>
                        <a href="/deposit" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-plus-circle"></i> Deposit
                        </a>
                        <a href="/logout" class="btn btn-outline">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt"></i> Logout
                        </a>
                    </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <div class="auth-buttons">
                        <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">
                            <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login
                        </a>
                        <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">
                            <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Register
                        </a>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Top Up Game Favorit Anda</h1>
            <p>Platform top up game terpercaya dengan harga terbaik. Nikmati pengalaman bermain game tanpa gangguan dengan layanan top up instan kami.</p>
            
            <div class="hero-buttons">
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="#games" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-gamepad"></i> Top Up Sekarang
                    </a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/register" class="btn btn-primary">
                        <i class="fas fa-user-plus"></i> Daftar Sekarang
                    </a>
                    <a href="/login" class="btn btn-outline">
                        <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login
                    </a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="games-section" id="games">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Game Populer</h2>
            
            <div class="games-grid">
                <% games.forEach(game => { %>
                    <div class="game-card">
                        <img src="<%= game.image %>" alt="<%= game.name %>" class="game-image">
                        <div class="game-info">
                            <h3 class="game-name"><%= game.name %></h3>
                            <p class="game-currency"><i class="fas fa-coins"></i> <%= game.currency %></p>
                            <% if (user) { %>
                                <a href="/topup/<%= game.id %>" class="btn btn-primary">
                                    <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> Top Up
                                </a>
                            <% } else { %>
                                <a href="/login" class="btn btn-primary">
                                    <i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login untuk Top Up
                                </a>
                            <% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }) %>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="features-section">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Kenapa Memilih Kami?</h2>
            
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Proses Instan</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Top up instan ke akun game Anda dalam hitungan detik setelah pembayaran berhasil.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Aman & Terpercaya</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Transaksi aman dengan enkripsi data dan perlindungan informasi pribadi Anda.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <div class="feature-icon">
                        <i class="fas fa-tags"></i>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Harga Terbaik</h3>
                    <p class="feature-description">Dapatkan harga top up terbaik dengan berbagai promo dan diskon menarik.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-links">
                <a href="#">Tentang Kami</a>
                <a href="#">Syarat & Ketentuan</a>
                <a href="#">Kebijakan Privasi</a>
                <a href="#">Bantuan</a>
            </div>
            
            <p class="copyright">&copy; 2023 PAYMU. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
